                        <interp inst="t18731124-31-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against the prisoner, for which see New Court, Wednesday</hi>).</p>
